examples.en: It adds up.
This adds to the expense.
Sales tax adds to the price.
Travel adds spice to your life.
Their fortune adds up to two million.
Goat's cheese adds extra bite to any pasta dish.
Lemon juice adds zing to drinks.
This adds a light note to the program.
Her performance adds flavor to the show.
So, your answer just adds up to a refusal.
Specialized software adds up the statistics.
This scandal adds more weight to their arguments.
Occasionally working from home adds variety to a job.
Spell-checking your document adds time to the process.
There are five of us using the phone so it all adds up.
Champagne always adds a touch of glamour to the occasion.
The aerugo of ancient metals adds greatly to their value.
The tall tower adds to the visual impact of the building.
